    "date": "2016-09-22T04:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Reducing Lead in Drinking Water Act\n\nThis bill amends the Safe Drinking Water Act to direct the Environmental Protection Agency to establish a grant program to remove lead service lines from public water systems.\n\nGrant recipients may use grant funds to assist low-income homeowners with replacing privately owned lead service lines."
